====擴展====
在1980年代晚期與1990年代早期，看見這些成立並漸漸引人關注的樂團不僅是和早期的表演者諸如Fugazi和Shellac這些有關，同時也包括[[Girls_Against_Boys|Girls Against Boys]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.punknews.org/review/7631 |title=Girls Against Boys - Venus Luxure No. 1 Baby |author=ngs091 |date=2008-09-12 |work=[[Punknews.org|Punknews.org]] |accessdate=2011-03-27 |archive-date=2009-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090722080419/http://www.punknews.org/review/7631 }}</ref>（他原本只是Brendan Canty和Eli Janney的side-project，但之後和Soulside幾位成員合作）、[[The_Jesus_Lizard|The Jesus Lizard]]<ref name="treblezine" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eyeweekly.com/liveeye/article/77127 |title=The Jesus Lizard @ The Phoenix, Nov. 12 |author=Bilton, Chris |date=2009-11-13 |work=EyeWeekly.com |accessdate=2011-03-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5ywPGoerc?url=http://www.eyeweekly.com/liveeye/article/77127 |archivedate=2011-05-25 }}</ref><ref name=Rhapsody>{{cite web |url=http://www.rhapsody.com/playlist/Pp.27114088 |title=Back to the '90s - Experiments in Post-Hardcore |author=Farrar, Justin |date=2009-04-03 |work=[[Rhapsody_(online_music_service)|Rhapsody Music]] |accessdate=2011-04-03 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303165132/http://www.rhapsody.com/playlist/Pp.27114088 }}</ref>（由幾位Scratch Acid前成員所成立的）、Quicksand<ref name="Quicksand">{{cite web |url=http://www.decibelmagazine.com/hall-of-fame/quicksand/ |title=Quicksand ''Slip'' |author=Bonazelli, Andrew |work=[[Decibel_(magazine)|Decibel]] |publisher=Red Flag Media |accessdate=2011-03-21 |archive-date=2010-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101014222124/http://www.decibelmagazine.com/hall-of-fame/quicksand/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>（創立自Youth of Today與Gorilla Biscuits的成員Walter Schreifels）、Rollins Band<ref>{{cite web |url=http://communities.washingtontimes.com/neighborhood/riffs-music/2010/sep/22/concert-review-kevin-seconds/ |title=Concert review: Kevin Seconds |author=Bradley, Stephen |date=2010-09-22 |work=[[The_Washington_Times|The Washington Times]] Communities - Riffs |accessdate=2011-03-21 |quote=[...] Where most punks from the '80s hardcore scene made the transition into hard rock or post hardcore outfits like Rollins Band and Fugazi, it still seems natural that he would make the jump into the acoustic side of things. [...] |archive-date=2011-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721184703/http://communities.washingtontimes.com/neighborhood/riffs-music/2010/sep/22/concert-review-kevin-seconds/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>（由前Black Flag主唱Henry Rollins所領軍）、[[Tar_(band)|Tar]]（由硬蕊團Blatant Dissent剩餘的成員組成的）<ref name=Rhapsody/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/p14449/biography |title= Tar - Biography |author=Huey, Steve |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |accessdate=2011-03-25}}</ref>與Slint<ref>{{cite web |url= http://altmusic.about.com/od/1990s/fr/slint.htm |title= Review of the Definitive Alternative Album Spiderland |author= Carew, Anthony |work= [[About.com|About.com]] |quote= [...] But, the second album by the post-hardcore Kentuckians sure didn't 'kick' anything; its influence rather devoid of immediacy. [...] |accessdate= 2011-03-21 |archive-date= 2011-09-29 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110929103649/http://altmusic.about.com/od/1990s/fr/slint.htm |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hipsterbookclub.com/features/influenceofanxiety/Jan11/index.html |title=The Influence of Anxiety: The Time Before |author=Parka, Dorothy |date=2011-01 |work=''Hipsterbookclub.com'' |accessdate=2011-03-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110727202347/http://www.hipsterbookclub.com/features/influenceofanxiety/Jan11/index.html |archivedate=2011-07-27 }}</ref>（包含一些Squirrel Bait的成員）。Shellac和[[Louisville,_Kentucky|Louisville]]的Slint被視為[[數學搖滾|數學搖滾]]（math rock）發展的影響樂團，<ref name="MathRockDOS">{{cite web |url=http://drownedinsound.com/in_depth/3205162-math-rock-family-tree--exploring-the-roots-of-foals |title=Math-Rock Family Tree: exploring the roots of Foals |author=Diver, Mike |date=2008-04-24 |work=[[Drowned_in_Sound|Drowned in Sound]] |accessdate=2011-03-25 |archive-date=2018-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180330155138/http://drownedinsound.com/in_depth/3205162-math-rock-family-tree--exploring-the-roots-of-foals |dead-url=no }}</ref>前者的特色為「在奇特時間點的拍號和侵略性的特色」，這成了描繪數學搖滾的「一個既定的見解」， <ref name="MathRockDOS"/>而後者呈現了「演奏性音樂從戲劇性的緊繃橋段流溢出來但又有固定的吉他結構樣式與重複性的打擊聲，這樣制式的方法」。<ref name="MathRockDOS"/>根據評論家Jason Arkeny，Slint的「靈巧，像是激進者操控音量、節奏與結構，使他們成為[[後龐克|後龐克]]運動的先驅。」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/slint-p14287/biography |title=Slint - Biography |author=Arkeny, Jason |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |accessdate=2011-03-25 |archive-date=2020-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200117054832/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/slint-p14287/biography }}</ref>

''Allmusic''曾提起這些較年輕的樂團「結束了中學時期所組的龐克樂團，成熟轉型成後硬蕊樂團」。<ref name=Posthardcoreallmusic/>在華盛頓特區，新樂團如Hoover（相關的樂團The Crownhate Ruin）、Circus Lupus、Bluetip與Smart Went Crazy都成了獨立廠牌Dischord的旗下成員。<ref name="DischordHist3">{{cite web |url=http://www.dischord.com/history/page03 |title=Dischord History |author=MacKaye |page=3 |accessdate=2011-03-26 |archive-date=2021-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515231835/https://dischord.com/history/page03 }}</ref>Hoover曾被雜誌記者Charles Spano譽為一個「在後硬蕊音樂上有極大影響力」得樂團。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/hoover-p292202/biography |title=Hoover - Biography |author=Spano, Charles |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |accessdate=2011-03-26 |archive-date=2010-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101117145919/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/hoover-p292202/biography }}</ref>在[[紐約|紐約]]，除了樂團Quicksand以外，後硬蕊樂團諸如Helmet<ref name=TopArtistsAllmusic/>、Unsane<ref name=TopArtistsAllmusic/><ref name=Rhapsody/>、Chavez<ref name="treblezine"/>與Texas Is the Reason<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.punknews.org/article/19888 |title=Interviews: Texas is the Reason |author=Aubin |date=2006-09-22 |work=[[Punknews.org|Punknews.org]] |accessdate=2011-03-26 |archive-date=2011-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110526081336/http://www.punknews.org/article/19888 }}</ref>也都紛紛出現。此外，Quicksand與Helmet樂團都和[[另類金屬|另類金屬]]有些關聯。<ref name="treblezine" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/quicksand-p20026/biography |title=Quicksand - Biography |last1=Ankeny |first1=Jason |last2=Prato |first2=Greg |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |accessdate=2011-03-26 |archive-date=2011-05-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5ywKD3NoF?url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/quicksand-p20026/biography |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/explore/style/d2697 |title=Explore: Alternative Metal |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |publisher= |accessdate=2011-03-26 |archive-date=2011-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110213161245/http://www.allmusic.com/explore/style/d2697 |dead-url=no }}</ref>芝加哥樂團Midwestern United States Chicago同樣也對數學搖滾有重要的影響<ref name="MathRockDOS"/>，同樣諸如Shellac、Tar、Trenchmouth這些樂團<ref name=TopArtistsAllmusic/>，以及獨立廠牌Jade Tree所發行的樂團Cap'n Jazz作品也都是。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.punknews.org/article/38899 |title=Contests: Win music and tickets from Cap'n Jazz |author=Aubin |date=2010-07-01 |work=[[Punknews.org|Punknews.org]] |accessdate=2011-03-26 |archive-date=2010-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100705104141/http://www.punknews.org/article/38899 }}</ref>（還有之後相繼的樂團Joan of Arc<ref>{{cite web |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C02E7D71731F93BA3575BC0A9659C8B63&pagewanted=6 |title=Pop and Jazz Guide |date=2003-08-08 |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |accessdate=2011-03-26}}</ref>，他們的發行也是透過Jade Tree唱片公司） Steve Huey主張Cap'n Jazz過去發行的專輯《Analphabetapolothology》幫助樂團將他們的影響力散播到「非原始聽眾群」，同時也他也認為，這個樂團也影響了獨立場景的Emo發展。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/capn-jazz-p278933/biography |title=Cap'n Jazz - Biography |author=Huey, Steve |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |accessdate=2011-03-26 |archive-date=2011-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110115041916/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/capn-jazz-p278933/biography }}</ref> 同樣在[[伊利諾州|伊利諾州]]的[[香檳_(伊利諾州)|香檳]]也以獨立樂團著名，給了樂團[[Hum|Hum]]、[[Braid|Braid]]和[[Poster_Children|Poster Children]]機會發展。<ref name="treblezine"/>在[[美國西北部|美國西北部]]也能見樂團如[[Karp|Karp]]、<ref name=Rhapsody/>[[Lync|Lync]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.internationalpopunderground.com/2011/02/kats-album-review-these-are-not-fall.html |title=Kat's Album Review - These Are Not Fall Colors by Lync |date=2011-02-04 |work=[[K_Records|Notes from the K Office]] |accessdate=2011-03-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110303035342/http://www.internationalpopunderground.com/2011/02/kats-album-review-these-are-not-fall.html |archivedate=2011-03-03 }}</ref>和[[Unwound|Unwound]]，<ref name=TopArtistsAllmusic/><ref name=Rhapsody/>這些樂團皆來自[[華盛頓州|華盛頓州]]的[[奧林匹亞_(華盛頓州)|奧林匹亞]]地需。後者的音樂被評論家John Bush認為是結合了「Sonic Youth更加粗重的噪音橋段」與「更甚Fugazi的少有旺盛天資」。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/unwound-p44884/biography |title=Unwound - Biography |author=Bush, John |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |accessdate=2011-03-27 |archive-date=2010-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101211183027/http://allmusic.com/artist/unwound-p44884/biography }}</ref>[[德克薩斯州|德州]]則有樂團The Jesus Lizard（之後轉陣到芝加哥）以及[[...And_You_Will_Know_Us_by_the_Trail_of_Dead|...And You Will Know Us by the Trail of Dead]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://communities.washingtontimes.com/neighborhood/riffs-music/2011/feb/8/music-review-and-you-shall-know-us-trail-dead/ |title=Music Review: ...And You Shall Know Us by the Trail of Dead - Tao of the Dead |author=Bradley, Stephen |date=2011-02-28 |work=[[The_Washington_Times|The Washington Times]] Communities - Riffs |accessdate=2011-04-01 |quote=The Trail of Dead has been known as something of a sprawling band ever since the band's first release in 1998. They've always been able to incorporate elements of noise rock and art rock into a post-hardcore foundation that allows for them to wander sonically not only from song to song but within each song itself and never losing the listener's interest in the song. |archive-date=2011-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721184734/http://communities.washingtontimes.com/neighborhood/riffs-music/2011/feb/8/music-review-and-you-shall-know-us-trail-dead/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他們來自[[奧斯丁|奧斯丁]]，還有從[[艾爾帕索_(德克薩斯州)|艾爾帕索]]來的[[At_the_Drive-In|At the Drive-In]]。<ref name="treblezine"/>最後個樂團正以他們在表演與音樂的熱力著名，他們「駕馭旋律的龐克riffsr，融合較寧靜的交錯點撥」。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/incasinoout-r373344/review |title=In/Casino/Out - At the Drive-In - Review |author=Butler, Blake |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |accessdate=2011-04-01 |archive-date=2012-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120414020837/http://allmusic.com/album/incasinoout-r373344/review }}</ref>

這個類型也在美國以外的地區看的到，如從[[于默奧|瑞典于默奧]]場景來的[[Refused|Refused]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://iheartau.com/news/refused-reunion-not-happening/ |title=Refused reunion not happening |date=2010-03-30 |work=[[Alternative_Ulster|I Heart AU]] |accessdate=2011-03-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100404015357/http://iheartau.com/news/refused-reunion-not-happening/ |archivedate=2010-04-04 }}</ref>這個樂團早期是以大量的硬蕊聲音而聞名，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/this-just-might-be-the-truth-r272829/review |title=This Just Might Be... the Truth - Refused - Review |author=Anderson, Jason |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |accessdate=2011-03-27}}</ref>1998年發行的專輯《The Shape of Punk to Come》，正是受樂團The Nation of Ulysses激發而成，<ref name="RefusedAV">{{cite web |url=http://www.avclub.com/articles/refused-the-shape-of-punk-to-come,41885/ |title=Refused: The Shape of Punk to Come - Music - Music Review |author=Heller, Jason |date=2010-06-08 |work=[[The_A.V._Club|The A.V. Club]] |publisher=[[The_Onion|Onion, Inc.]] |accessdate=2011-03-27 |archive-date=2013-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131026011158/http://www.avclub.com/articles/refused-the-shape-of-punk-to-come,41885/ }}</ref><ref name="ShapePunkAllmusic">{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/the-shape-of-punk-to-come-r378774/review |title=The Shape of Punk to Come - Refused - Review |author=Butler, Blake |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |accessdate=2011-03-27 |archive-date=2012-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120501132745/http://allmusic.com/album/the-shape-of-punk-to-come-r378774/review }}</ref>同時加入[[氛圍音樂|氛圍音樂]]、爵士式的breakdown、<ref name="ShapePunkAllmusic"/>金屬和[[電子音樂|電子音樂]]進去他們的硬蕊聲音。

==與電音融合的後硬蕊==
一些現代的後硬蕊樂團，開始將這種音樂與[[電子音樂|電子音樂]]（[[Electronica|Electronica]]）結合，<ref name=ISSaa>{{cite web |last=Birchmeier |first=Jason |title=I See Stars - Biography |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/i-see-stars-p1122695 |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |publisher=[[Rovi_Corporation|Rovi Corporation]] |accessdate=2011-04-25 |archive-date=2010-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101211232654/http://allmusic.com/artist/i-see-stars-p1122695 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=ISS/><ref name=SkyAA>{{cite web |last=Birchmeier |first=Jason |title=Sky Eats Airplane - Biography |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/sky-eats-airplane-p1001468/biography |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |publisher=[[Rovi_Corporation|Rovi Corporation]] |accessdate=2011-04-25 |archive-date=2012-12-14 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CtpqZGiv?url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/sky-eats-airplane-mn0000657920 |dead-url=no }}</ref>創造出所謂的[[電子蕊|電子蕊]]（Electronicore）或混音蕊（Synthcore）<ref name=AWZUM>{{cite web |last=Pio |first=Gabriel [http://thenewreview.net/staff#gabriel31 (Staff member)] |title=I See Stars - ''The End of the World Party'' |url=http://thenewreview.net/reviews/i-see-stars-the-end-of-the-world-party |publisher=TheNewReview.net |accessdate=2011-04-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110223162300/http://thenewreview.net/reviews/i-see-stars-the-end-of-the-world-party |archivedate=2011-02-23 }}</ref><ref name=UTGR/>樂團利用[[金屬蕊|金屬蕊]]的BreakDown、[[吼腔|吼腔]]結合[[混音|混音]]、電子音效與Auto-Tune處理。<ref name=AWZUM/><ref name=UTGR>{{cite web |last=Duffy |first=Grace [http://underthegunreview.net/staff/ (Staff member)] |title=REVIEW: I SEE STARS – END OF THE WORLD PARTY |url=http://underthegunreview.net/2011/03/01/review-i-see-stars-end-of-the-world-party/ |publisher=Under the Gun Reviews |accessdate=2011-04-25 |archive-date=2011-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724115757/http://underthegunreview.net/2011/03/01/review-i-see-stars-end-of-the-world-party/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=AASaa/>這些團體多源自[[英國|英國]]、<ref name=APaa>{{cite web |last=Freeman |first=Phil |title=Asking Alexandria - ''Reckless & Relentless'' |url=http://www.altpress.com/reviews/entry/asking_alexandria_-_reckless_relentless/ |work=AltPress.com |publisher=[[Alternative_Press|Alternative Press]] |accessdate=2011-04-25 |archive-date=2021-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328165356/https://www.altpress.com/reviews/asking_alexandria_-_reckless_relentless/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=StandS/>[[美國|美國]]<ref name=ISSaa/><ref name=SkyAA/>與加拿大。<ref name=AASaa>{{cite web |last=Heaney |first=Gregory |title=Abandon All Ships - Biography |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/abandon-all-ships-p2229989 |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |publisher=[[Rovi_Corporation|Rovi Corporation]] |accessdate=2011-04-25 |archive-date=2010-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101115112504/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/abandon-all-ships-p2229989 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[Sumerian唱片|Sumerian唱片]]提到：「近期有太多的「[[電音|電音]]/[[硬蕊|硬蕊]]」音樂了。」<ref name=ISS>{{cite web |url=http://www.sumerianrecords.com/artists.php?band=1039 |title=I See Stars on Sumerian Records |publisher=[[Sumerian_Records|Sumerian Records]] |accessdate=2009-11-01 |archive-date=2009-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090301014345/http://sumerianrecords.com/artists.php?band=1039 }}</ref>他們旗下的樂團[[I_See_Stars|I See Stars]]被認為是這種音樂類型的始祖，<ref name="ISSaa"/><ref name=ISS/><ref name=AWZUM/><ref name=UTGR/>樂團首張專輯《3D》正是混音蕊（Synthcore）音樂中最熱門的。<ref name=AWZUM/>其他將後硬蕊或[[金屬蕊|金屬蕊]]與[[電子音樂|電子音樂]]結合的樂團有[[Abandon_All_Ships|Abandon All Ships]]、<ref name=AWZUM/><ref name=AASaa/>[[Attack_Attack!|Attack Attack!]]、<ref name=AWZUM/><ref name=AAtv>{{cite web |last=Hidden |first=Chris |title=ATTACK ATTACK! - ''ATTACK ATTACK!'' |url=http://www.rocksound.tv/reviews/article/attack-attack-attack-attack |work=[[Rock_Sound|Rock Sound Magazine]] |publisher=Rock Sound |accessdate=2011-04-25 |archive-date=2021-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328165356/https://www.rocksound.tv/reviews/read/attack-attack-attack-attack |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[Asking_Alexandria|Asking Alexandria]]、<ref name=AWZUM/><ref name=APaa/><ref name=StandS>{{cite web |last=Freeman |first=Phil |title=''Stand Up and Scream'' |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/stand-up-and-scream-r1634086/review |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |publisher=[[Rovi_Corporation|Rovi Corporation]] |accessdate=2011-04-25 |archive-date=2020-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200528162157/https://www.allmusic.com/album/stand-up-and-scream-mw0000824503 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[Enter_Shikari|Enter Shikari]]、<ref name=kingtrance>{{cite web |url=http://puregrainaudio.com/features/enter-shikari |title=Enter Shikari: "Kings of Trancecore" |publisher=PureGrainAudio |accessdate=2010-04-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100203224912/http://puregrainaudio.com/features/enter-shikari |archivedate=2010-02-03 }}</ref><ref name=Common>{{cite web |last=Carino |first=Paula |title=''Common Dreads'' |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/common-dreads-r1596479 |work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]] |publisher=[[Rovi_Corporation|Rovi Corporation]] |accessdate=2011-04-25 |archive-date=2010-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101205025315/http://allmusic.com/album/common-dreads-r1596479 |dead-url=no }}</ref>與[[Sky_Eats_Airplane|Sky Eats Airplane]]。<ref name="SkyAA"/>

